1:21:45.857 --> 1:21:47.554
Fuck! Fuck!

1:21:47.598 --> 1:21:49.556
- What the hell is going on?
- It's nothing!

1:21:49.600 --> 1:21:51.950
The emergency generator
will kick on.

1:21:51.994 --> 1:21:55.258
♪

