1:21:59.740 --> 1:22:01.742
[groaning]

1:22:07.052 --> 1:22:08.053
There.

1:22:08.097 --> 1:22:09.968
♪

1:22:10.012 --> 1:22:11.970
[thunder]

1:22:12.014 --> 1:22:14.755
[gasping]

1:22:26.985 --> 1:22:28.900
[thunder crashes]

1:22:30.467 --> 1:22:32.034
Karl.

1:22:32.077 --> 1:22:35.298
These are not Tyler's
most recent X-Rays we did.

1:22:35.341 --> 1:22:37.213
[thunder crashes]

1:22:39.780 --> 1:22:40.999
They're in my study

1:22:41.043 --> 1:22:42.479
on my desk.

1:22:43.784 --> 1:22:45.830
[groaning]

1:22:45.873 --> 1:22:47.745
[thunder]

1:22:50.574 --> 1:22:52.141
Shall we start
with the girl?

1:22:53.055 --> 1:22:54.012
Yes.

1:22:59.539 --> 1:23:02.368
♪

1:23:05.676 --> 1:23:08.331
