9-1-1, what's your emergency?

1:23:08.374 --> 1:23:10.028
My daughter...

1:23:10.072 --> 1:23:12.988
[dramatic music swells ♪]

1:23:14.380 --> 1:23:16.208
[operator]
I can't hear you, ma'am.
Can you speak louder?

1:23:16.252 --> 1:23:19.995
He's going to kill
my daughter.

1:23:21.909 --> 1:23:24.956
[thunder]

1:23:25.000 --> 1:23:26.566
[operator]
Are you okay, ma'am?

1:23:26.610 --> 1:23:27.959
Ma'am?

1:23:28.003 --> 1:23:29.743
Hello?

1:23:29.787 --> 1:23:33.051
I need you to talk to me.
Are you in danger?

1:23:33.095 --> 1:23:34.226
Are you alone right now?

1:23:34.270 --> 1:23:37.012
Ma'am?

1:23:37.055 --> 1:23:41.407
[ominous muffled rumbling]

1:23:49.589 --> 1:23:52.810
It's time for you to return
to the angels in Heaven.

1:23:56.509 --> 1:23:59.556
[crash]

1:23:59.599 --> 1:24:02.167
[dark, ominous music ♪]

1:24:02.211 --> 1:24:05.040
[muffled heartbeat]

1:24:10.306 --> 1:24:12.395
[snorts deeply]

1:24:13.135 --> 1:24:15.093
[moans]

1:24:16.877 --> 1:24:20.229
[thunder]

1:24:21.752 --> 1:24:24.015
[snorts]

1:24:27.149 --> 1:24:29.194
