1:24:31.501 --> 1:24:33.546
[intense, chilling music ♪]

1:24:33.590 --> 1:24:35.635
[growls]

1:24:35.679 --> 1:24:38.334
[grunting]

1:24:40.684 --> 1:24:44.383
[screaming]

1:24:44.427 --> 1:24:47.691
[intense rock music ♪]

1:24:47.734 --> 1:24:48.953
Olga?!

1:24:48.996 --> 1:24:50.998
♪

1:24:51.042 --> 1:24:52.913
Maria, stay with the surgeon.

1:24:52.957 --> 1:24:54.785
Everyone else, come with me.

1:24:54.828 --> 1:24:58.354
[thunder]

1:24:58.397 --> 1:25:00.356
[screaming]

1:25:00.399 --> 1:25:03.620
Jesus Christ.

1:25:03.663 --> 1:25:05.100
Nina.

1:25:05.143 --> 1:25:07.102
♪

1:25:07.145 --> 1:25:09.016
I don't understand.

1:25:09.060 --> 1:25:11.802
She was on a heavy dosage
of diamorphine.

1:25:11.845 --> 1:25:14.021
There's no way that she could--

1:25:14.065 --> 1:25:15.153
[thunder]

1:25:15.197 --> 1:25:17.851
Oh, Nina...

1:25:17.895 --> 1:25:20.985
Nina, Nina...

1:25:21.028 --> 1:25:24.162
Nina.
[thunder]

1:25:24.206 --> 1:25:29.124
♪

1:25:34.825 --> 1:25:36.043
If she wants to get
to her daughter,

1:25:36.087 --> 1:25:38.829
she's got to have access
to the second floor.

1:25:38.872 --> 1:25:40.091
Buchannan.
- Yeah?

1:25:40.135 --> 1:25:41.962
I want you to cover
the staircase.

1:25:42.006 --> 1:25:44.008
Maybe we should just give her
her daughter back,
for Christ's sake?

1:25:44.051 --> 1:25:46.053
Nephew, I love you,

1:25:46.097 --> 1:25:48.012
you got potential,
but if you ever wanna
be like me,

1:25:48.055 --> 1:25:51.058
you better grow some balls
tonight!

1:25:51.102 --> 1:25:53.017
It's a battlefield
out there, kid.

1:25:53.060 --> 1:25:56.412
That woman and her daughter
are nothing but cannon fodder!

1:25:58.022 --> 1:26:01.417
You cover the elevator.
You see her,
and you shoot to kill!

1:26:01.460 --> 1:26:03.158
I had enough cocaine
in that urn

1:26:03.201 --> 1:26:04.550
to kill a goddamn horse.

1:26:04.594 --> 1:26:06.726
Sooner or later,
her heart's gonna give out.

1:26:06.770 --> 1:26:09.076
[thunder]
[clattering]

1:26:10.556 --> 1:26:13.037
All right, Cranston,
you cover the perimeter.

1:26:13.080 --> 1:26:16.388
The rest of you, I want you
to look everywhere fast!

1:26:16.432 --> 1:26:19.478
I don't want my son waiting
any longer than he has to!

1:26:19.522 --> 1:26:21.611
[growls]

1:26:21.654 --> 1:26:24.179
[breathes deeply]

1:26:27.007 --> 1:26:29.923
[monitor beeping]

1:26:33.144 --> 1:26:35.233
I didn't sign up
for this madness.

1:26:36.495 --> 1:26:38.193
I'm going out for a cigarette.

1:26:45.243 --> 1:26:47.245
[thunder]

1:26:47.289 --> 1:26:48.290
[gun clicks]

1:26:50.683 --> 1:26:53.338
[rain pattering]

1:26:53.382 --> 1:26:56.123
[thunder roaring]

1:26:56.167 --> 1:26:58.691
[clatter]

1:27:07.047 --> 1:27:09.746
[ominous ambience]

1:27:09.789 --> 1:27:11.138
Stairs.

1:27:16.840 --> 1:27:21.975
[eerie nursery music ♪]

1:27:30.245 --> 1:27:32.595
[ominous ambience builds]

1:27:32.638 --> 1:27:38.122
[thunder]

1:27:38.165 --> 1:27:41.168
[wind howling]

1:27:46.696 --> 1:27:50.265
[rain pounding]

1:27:53.093 --> 1:27:54.573
The window!

1:27:54.617 --> 1:27:57.184
♪

1:27:58.229 --> 1:27:59.926
[thunder]

1:27:59.970 --> 1:28:01.276
What the--

1:28:02.929 --> 1:28:04.191
Mom?!

1:28:04.235 --> 1:28:05.192
[screaming]

1:28:05.236 --> 1:28:07.543
[intense music ♪]

1:28:07.586 --> 1:28:10.763
[crying out]

1:28:12.156 --> 1:28:13.375
Stay.

1:28:15.986 --> 1:28:19.206
[growls]

1:28:19.250 --> 1:28:21.818
[dramatic music ♪]

1:28:26.257 --> 1:28:29.391
[thunder]

1:28:31.349 --> 1:28:34.178
Reign! Bad men!
Attack!

1:28:34.221 --> 1:28:35.788
[barking]

1:28:36.223 --> 1:28:38.269
[thunder]

1:28:38.313 --> 1:28:41.272
♪

1:28:44.623 --> 1:28:47.060
[growling, barking]

1:28:47.104 --> 1:28:48.888
[screaming]

1:28:48.932 --> 1:28:50.934
[crying out]

1:28:56.026 --> 1:28:58.202
♪

1:28:58.245 --> 1:29:02.337
[barking]
[screaming]

1:29:03.425 --> 1:29:07.124
Guys, what the fuck
is going on here?!

1:29:07.167 --> 1:29:08.473
♪

1:29:08.517 --> 1:29:10.388
Fuck this.

1:29:10.432 --> 1:29:13.826
[thunder]

1:29:13.870 --> 1:29:17.743
♪

1:29:31.583 --> 1:29:35.457
[grunting]

1:29:36.327 --> 1:29:38.416
Keller?!

1:29:38.460 --> 1:29:40.287
Keller!

1:29:40.331 --> 1:29:43.334
[crying out]
[thunder]

1:29:46.337 --> 1:29:47.469
I'm sorry!

1:29:47.512 --> 1:29:50.297
[stab]

1:29:58.175 --> 1:29:59.263
What are you doing?

1:29:59.306 --> 1:30:00.873
I've had enough.

1:30:00.917 --> 1:30:02.266
I'm leaving.

1:30:02.309 --> 1:30:03.920
Is there a back door?

1:30:03.963 --> 1:30:05.312
I don't want
to go down there.

1:30:05.356 --> 1:30:08.098
You can't leave!
Tyler needs you!

1:30:08.141 --> 1:30:09.926
Can't you hear?
Men are dying!

1:30:09.969 --> 1:30:11.449
[grunts]

1:30:11.493 --> 1:30:13.538
[ominous ambience]

1:30:13.582 --> 1:30:16.802
[thunder]

1:30:19.022 --> 1:30:21.503
[panting]

1:30:31.513 --> 1:30:32.339
[thunder]

1:30:32.383 --> 1:30:34.298
Somebody?

1:30:34.341 --> 1:30:35.952
Somebody talk to me!

1:30:35.995 --> 1:30:37.910
[generator rumbling]

1:30:37.954 --> 1:30:39.869
Guys?!

1:30:39.912 --> 1:30:42.698
What the hell
is going on?

1:30:42.741 --> 1:30:45.962
[panting]

1:30:48.921 --> 1:30:51.315
[growl]
[screams]

1:30:51.358 --> 1:30:52.838
That's it.
I'm out of here.

1:30:52.882 --> 1:30:55.014
Please, please,
I beg you.

1:30:55.058 --> 1:30:56.363
I'm sorry.

1:30:56.407 --> 1:30:57.974
